trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle"></xref> objects in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.

trans-unit.source: The SubMenuStyleCollection class is used to store and manage a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> objects in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen SubMenuStyleCollection brukes til å lagre og behandle en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>objekter i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control uses the SubMenuStyleCollection class as the underlying data type of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollen bruker SubMenuStyleCollection-klassen som underliggende datatypen for det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property provides additional style choices in addition to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DynamicMenuStyle%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>egenskapen gir ekstra stil valg i tillegg til den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuStyle%2A>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DynamicMenuStyle%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DynamicMenuStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>

trans-unit.source: The first style in the SubMenuStyleCollection collection corresponds to the submenu style for the first level of the menu.
trans-unit.target: Den første malen i samlingen SubMenuStyleCollection tilsvarer undermenyen-stil for det første nivået i listen.

trans-unit.source: The second style in the collection corresponds to the submenu style for the second level of the menu, and so on.
trans-unit.target: Andre stilen i samlingen tilsvarer undermenyen-stil for nivå for meny- og så videre.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property is most often used to generate a navigation menu, like a Web site map, where menu items at a certain level should have the same appearance, regardless of whether they have submenus.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>egenskapen brukes vanligvis til å generere en navigasjonsmenyen, som et kart for webområdet hvor menyelementer på et bestemt nivå må ha samme utseendet, uavhengig om de har undermenyer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>
